extends base.pug

block style 
    style
        include ../static/style.css


block content


    div(class="container")
        h2(class="my-3") About us
        div(class="accordionExample.accordion")

        //- First Accordion Item
        div(class="accordion-item")
            h2(class="accordion-header")
                button(class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne")
                    strong Analyze your text
            
            div(class="collapseOne accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample")
                div(class="accordion-body")
                    p Textutils gives you a way to analyze your text quickly and efficiently. Be it word count or chracter count.

        //- Second Accordion Item
        div(class="accordion-item")
            h2(class="accordion-header")
                button(class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo")
                    strong Free to use

            div(id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample")
                div(class="accordion-body")
                    p Textutils is a free character counter tool that provides instant character count and word count statistics for a given text. TextUtils reports the number of words and characters. Thus it s suitable for writing text with word/character limit.      

        //- Third Accordion Item
        div(class="accordion-item")
            h2(class="accordion-header")
                button(class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree")
                    strong Browser Compatible
            div(id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample")
                div(class="accordion-body")
                    p This word counter software works in any web browsers such as Chrome, Firefox, Internet Explorer, Safari, Opera. It suits to count characters in facebook, blog, book, excel document, pdf document, essays, etc.


block scripts 
    script(src='../static/index.js')